  "prompt": "Which is the best C programming training institute in Bhubaneswar?",
  "response": "Determining the \"best\" C programming training institute can be subjective and depends on various factors such as course content, instructor expertise, infrastructure, placement opportunities, and student feedback. Here are a few popular options you might consider in Bhubaneswar:\n\n1. **Naresh IT**: Known for a wide range of programming courses including C, they often have experienced instructors and comprehensive course materials.\n\n2. **LIT (Lakhotia Institute of Technology)**: They offer various IT courses and have good infrastructure with experienced faculty.\n\n3. **CTTC (Central Tool Room & Training Centre)**: Known for its technical programs and practical training, CTTC offers various courses including programming languages.\n\n4. **Orangus**: They provide training in various programming languages including C, and have good student feedback.\n\n5. **Aptech Computer Education**: A well-known name in IT training, Aptech has branches across India including Bhubaneswar, offering various programming courses.\n\nIt is recommended to visit these institutes, talk to current students, and review the curriculum and placement records before making a decision. Additionally, online reviews and testimonials can provide further insights into the quality of training provided.",
